<ul><li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.haskell.org/">HaskellWiki</a>
</li><li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cs.tufts.edu/~nr/c--/index.html">C--</a>
</li><li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wiki.haskell.org/Calling_Haskell_from_C">Calling Haskell from C</a>
</li><li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.macs.hw.ac.uk/~dsg/gph/docs/4.06/users_guide/glasgow-ccalls.html">Calling C from Haskell</a>
</li><li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://downloads.haskell.org/~ghc/7.8.3/docs/html/users_guide/code-generators.html">GHC Backends</a>
</li><li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.cse.unsw.edu.au/~chak/haskell/ffi/ffi.pdf">The Haskell Foreign Function Interface</a>
</li></ul>

